sooner
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a lazy dog that would sooner lie in the sun than work [or would sooner have its owner do the work.]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
